Class Feed

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.Feed

  • public class Feed
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages feed from one URL. This also stores the slot on the UI tabs on which position it's at. YOU MUST HANDLE THESE EXCEPTIONS IN THE CONTROLLER ITSELF SINCE THIS CLASS CANNOT RETURN THE ERROR ITSELF!
    Author:
    Seth Chick, hnn727
